name: Unsupervised-Machine-Learning-Mall-Customer-Data-Market-Segmentation
description: In this project, I work with an unlabelled mall customer dataset, containing Customer ID, age, gender, annual income, and spending score. My objective: understand customer preferences for targeted strategies. Using K-means clustering and PCA, I aim to segment the market and visualise data.

name: WildDuckPipe
description: Simple pipeline to process astronomical imagens taken on the OPD/LNA (MG - Brazil). It perforns intrumental reduction in a single command (given proper FITS headers),  has tooling for accelerating quality control,  can perform  individual or time series photometry in one command and has procedures for doing differential photometry.

name: Project8_IMDB_Movies_Reviews_Clustering
description: This GitHub repository contains the IMDb Movies Reviews Clustering project, which uses Natural Language Processing techniques and K-Means clustering to analyze IMDb movie reviews. Explore this repository to discover insights from textual data and visualize the hierarchical structure of movie opinions.
